@zgramana  I have verified the unit test in this PR, and it runs fine with latest Calcite.
Therefore, as I suspected, it seems the bug has been fixed as a side effect of [CALCITE-5061](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CALCITE-5061), so I'll close the Jira [CALCITE-5051](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CALCITE-5051).
Shall we close this PR?

@chunweilei Thanks for your review.
> Should we add a test?

I'm not sure about this, as existing benchmarks all do not have tests, I think maybe we do not need it?

@julianhyde  Thanks for your suggestions.
I've fixed almost all the points you raised.
I would fixed the order by conversion logical, including support null_first/ null_last, and combine it with `convertOrderItem ` in the next commit of this pr.

